        {
          "id": "1258120",
          "replier": {
            "username": "Streptopelia",
            "uid": "115196"
          },
          "date": "2024-04-16",
          "content": "@fb_china_today:中国的屏蔽成功率本来就不是100%，你可以看一下 Even Censors Have a Backup: Examining China's Double HTTPS Censorship System\nhttps://geneva.cs.umd.edu/papers/2021-foci-censors-have-backup.pdf\n浏览器不够快，想耗多点资源应该用程序高速发送client hello，顺便说一下\"pincong.rocks\"从中国外面发进来也能触发TCP RST。"
        }
